('CHEN, Chongxi (1988) : [Analytic models of groundwater flows to karst springs]. ', 1988, 'Carsologia sinica vol. 7 (nr. 3) : 247-252 (chines.; engl. summ.).', 'Four conceptional analytic models, which describe the laminar or turbulent groundwater flow to karstic springs have been established respectively. The first two models show one dimentional flow and radial flow in accordance with the Darcy (linear) flow. The other two give the expression of one dimensional, resp. radial flow following non linear law', 1.120, NULL, NULL, 'China         ', '1988.0032', 198800320, 'Min LIN;Chongxi CHEN; ; ; ; ; ; ; ; '),
